properties.headline: FLOODING - COOPERNOOK TO GLENTHORNE Pacific Highway between George Gibson Drive, Coopernook and Manning River Drive/Old Bar Road
properties.otherAdvice:
In Cundletown, the Pacific Hwy on-ramps from Main St/Princes St have been closed and access to the highway has been restricted.

A number of local roads in this area, including Lansdowne Rd and George Gibson Dr, are also closed due to flooding. At this stage, there is no suitable diversion.

properties.headline: FLOODING - WINDSOR Macquarie Street between Brabyn Street AND Bell Street
properties.adviceB: Exercise caution; Do not drive through floodwater
properties.diversions:
Northbound:Argyle St, Fairey Rd, Mileham St, Hawkesbury Valley Way to rejoin Macquarie St.

Southbound: Hawkesbury Valley Way, Mileham St, Fairey Rd, Argyle St to rejoin Macquarie St.

Heavy vehicles are being allowed through under escort.
